Detailed Description

The configuration information for a connection with a CRANE server (collector).

final int com::xacct::CRANE::collector::ConnectionConfig::getConnectRetryTimeout (   )  [inline]
 

How long to wait for between individual attempts to get ProtocolInfo in milliseconds. If no response is received within this time, another attempt will be made. The total number of attempts is controlled by connectTimeout.
